===Verb===
'''separate''' (''Inflected forms'': separated, separating, separates)
#to divide into parts, [[split]].
#:'''''Separate''' the articles from the headings.''
#(intransitive) to come apart; to move apart.
#:''The sauce will '''separate''' if you don't keep stirring.''
#to keep apart; to be between.
#:''If the kids get too noisy, '''separate''' them for a few minutes.''

